{
  "chapter": 110,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙以董马痴身份护送纪嫣然和田氏姊妹出城。李园率家将追来纠缠，被乌果断然拦阻，只得悻悻离去。纪嫣然暗中换装随队，项少龙安排邹衍和田氏姊妹由精兵团护送经韩境赴咸阳。随后项少龙等在密林设伏，千余名城卫以弓箭伏击严平率领的赵墨行者三百人。项少龙亲自出战，与严平展开决斗，以墨氏三大杀招之“攻守兼资”击败严平，一剑刺穿其胸膛，为元宗报仇。严平临死前方认出董匡就是项少龙。战后项少龙回城，滕翼汇报已布置好擒拿叛将赵明雄的计划，齐人正从秘道潜入，一切按计划进行。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "路人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那就是董马痴了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "百姓",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这才是真正的英雄好汉呢！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我才不在外面等候你，说什么都没用的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "你怎么脱身来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "让干爹去应付他们好了，人家才没有那个精神。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "韩闯刚才告诉我，李园率领着五百多名家将要送我到魏境去，他们刻下正在城外等候人家，怎样应付才好？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "放心吧！他只是藉送你为名，趁机离开邯郸，好与今晚城内发生的事划清界线，事后才返来查看结果。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tian_shi_zi_mei",
      "text": "路途上乖乖地听邹先生的话，很快你们便可到咸阳，那时我们又可以在一起生活了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zou_yan",
      "text": "先生珍重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zou_yan",
      "speaker_name": "邹衍",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "天下间，怕没有你做不来的事了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "三弟猜得不错，嫣然公然由东门出城，大出严平意料之外，现在他们正全速赶来，快要到达了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "任他们怎么想，也猜不到赵人竟会对付他们，还得到孝成王的同意。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "text": "李园这小子有没有回城？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "他自己往齐人营地去，只派十多人来追踪嫣然，全给我们宰掉。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们要杀得他们片甲不留，绝不留情。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "乌卓",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "放心吧！千多人去伏击三百人，又是出其不意，他们哪有活命的机会，就算有人逃掉，回城亦只是送死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "嫣然的苦难终于过去，由今天开始，和夫郎并肩作战，同进共退，生死不渝。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "严平",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董匡！这算是什么一回事？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_yan_ping",
      "text": "巨子不知自爱，竟与赵穆合谋造反，大王命本将军来取尔之命。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "严平",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董匡！是英雄的就凭手中之剑来取本人之命。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_yan_ping",
      "text": "巨子既有此意，让董某人成全你。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "严平",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你是……",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_yan_ping",
      "text": "这一剑是元宗送给你的。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "元兄！你在天若有灵，好该安息。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今天城卫大批调动，我故意弄得乱成一团，其实乱的是赵明雄他们的人马，我们的人都迅速聚集到指定的地点。更由于我故意把大批兵卒调往城外，除我之外，没有人可弄清楚真正的分布。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "有二哥指挥大局，没有人会不放心的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天一入黑，我们立采取行动，把叛党所有将领擒下，又借口三弟来了，实施全城戒严，以免发生事时误伤无辜的老百姓。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为何尚未有我出现的消息传来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "荆俊已摸清楚北面秘道的情况，赵明雄把出口所在官署的人全调出来，改由自己的亲兵把守，他本人坐镇北门兵卫所，就算我们把赵明雄宰了来吃，他在官署的手下怕仍懵然不知。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "小俊尚有什么消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "午后起，齐人开始穿过背风山的洞穴，悄悄潜入林区，小俊不敢冒险入林探查，但可以想象入黑后他们会在赵明雄的掩护下，渡过护城河，由秘道潜入城内。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若齐人发觉掩护他们的竟全是我们的人，不知会有何感想？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "定然深感荣幸！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guo",
      "speaker_name": "乌果",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "赵偏将传来消息，发现项少龙的踪迹。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 110,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    }
  ],
